                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/9815" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">STR-2466</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">830 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">“引进来，走出去”：数智化赋能宇通客车全生命周期成本管理</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">&quot;Bringing In and Going Global&quot;: Digital Intelligence Empowers Lifecycle Cost Management at Yutong Bus</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">蒲丹琳，徐全亮，严琦，胡文博</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">湖南大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">宇通客车股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">交通运输业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门/总经理办公室</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">23 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">全生命周期成本（LCC）管理；数智化转型；新能源客车；价值链</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Life Cycle Cost (LCC) Management; Digital-Intelligent Transformation; New Energy Bus; Value Chain</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">在客车行业竞争加剧以及全球低碳转型背景下，宇通客车坚持全生命周期成本（LCC）管理，通过数智化转型实现逆势突围。面对高铁替代效应与行业同质化竞争，宇通客车于2013年率先推行LCC管理，实现“引进来”，同客户实现价值共创。2017年后为应对补贴退坡与需求萎缩，宇通客车深化智能网联平台、睿控E系统等数智化技术应用，2022年实现LCC管理向超基因价值链升级，依托技术优势“走出去”，拓展了海外市场，并推动行业生态共建。本案例可引导学员思考数智化技术如何赋能传统制造企业升级价值链、应对行业危机，以及LCC管理与产业发展的协同逻辑，为制造业转型升级提供实践参考。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Amid intensifying competition in the coach industry and global low-carbon transition, Yutong Bus has adhered to the management of the life cycle cost (LCC) and achieved a breakthrough against the odds through digital-intelligent transformation. Confronted with high-speed rail substitution and homogeneous competition in the industry, Yutong pioneered the LCC management in 2013, achieving &quot;bringing in&quot; and co-creating value with customers. After 2017, to cope with the decline in subsidies and shrinking demand, Yutong Bus deepened the application of digital and intelligent technologies such as the intelligent network connection platform and the RuiKong E system. In 2022, it upgraded LCC management to the super gene value chain, relying on its technological advantages to &quot;go global&quot;, expanding overseas markets and promoting the co-construction of the industry ecosystem. This case can guide students to think about how digital and intelligent technologies empower traditional manufacturing enterprises to upgrade their value chains and deal with industry crises, as well as the collaborative logic between LCC management and industrial development, providing practical references for the transformation and upgrading of the manufacturing industry.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《战略管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">（1）价值链；（2）全生命周期成本管理；（3）利益相关者理论；（4）客户生命周期价值；（5）数智化转型</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-09</td>
                            </tr>
